### Retrieve specific priority question [GET /priority-questions/{id}]
+ Parameters

    + id (string, required) - Id of the priority question
    
+ Request

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer {accesstoken}
            cid: 05e230bf-a9cf-4b31-bc54-d3a995f62526

+ Response 200 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "SUCCESS",
                "data": {
                    "priorityQuestion": {
                        "id": "Nzc4OGM4NmQtOGU4My1lNTExLWFlZWYtMDA1MDU2OTgwMzkzfFE",
                        "description": "Is the leak containable?",
                        "priorityAnswers": [
                            "9faccffa-8f83-e511-aeef-005056980393",
                            "979ba679-9283-e511-aeef-005056980393",
                            "67925707-9383-e511-a87d-005056982288"
                        ]
                    }
                },
                "errors": [],
                "meta": {}
            }
            
+ Response 401 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "FAIL",
                "data": {},
                "errors": [
                    {
                        "code": "authorize",
                        "message": "access_denied"
                    }
                ],
                "meta": {}
            }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "FAIL",
                "data": {},
                "errors": [
                    {
                        "code": "id",
                        "message": "error.client.id.invalid"
                    }
                ],
                "meta": {}
            }

+ Response 500 (application/json)

            {
                "status": "FAIL",
                "data": {},
                "errors": [
                    {
                        "code": "server.error.internal",
                        "message": "An internal error while processing request."
                    }
                ],
                "meta": {}
            }

